title: SPOOKS of Spooky Week #1
body:
I really like watching DnP play scary games and shit their pants but I absolutely HATE being jumpscared myself. So I made a list of everything from mildly scary to really harrowing so you can hide behind a pillow/scroll down to the comment section/go to another tab etc. while watching. Here you go:


Dan and Phil play: GRANNY

Terrible graphics. Location is an old scary house. You have to sneak out without  Granny finding you and hitting you with a baseball bat.

2:50 they show the icon of the game (the granny) and she looks quite terrifying

3:43 full body pic of Granny

5:58 first jumpscare!

7:33 Granny comes and hits you

8:05 she comes into the room

9:00 jumpscare. this one got me good

9:47 Granny enters the room again

11:28 Granny comes and hits you

12:07 jumpscare!

12:14 scary sequence

12:27 you can see her up close. harrowing.

13:26 scary figure

summary: I’m seeing a lot of worried posts about Phil’s pub tweet that are like “why was Phil at a pub?!?!!?!” And I feel like this is a...
body:
I’m seeing a lot of worried posts about Phil’s pub tweet that are like “why was Phil at a pub?!?!!?!” And I feel like this is a situation where a pub is something different in England than it is here.


A pub is a restaurant/bar combo. Y’know, somewhere you might go for dinner, or to hang out with friends. Normal place for a grown man to appear, not cause for concern.


British Phandom, True or false?

summary: are you interested in purchasing the 2019 D&P art calendar? then please let us know so we can calculate the final price! there...
body:
are you interested in purchasing the 2019 D&P art calendar? then please let us know so we can calculate the final price!

there will be two options; a physical A3 copy and a digital download. they will both cost money seeing as it’s for charity, but of course the digital version will be cheaper

please let us know which version you are interested in here

the more people are interested, the less each calendar will cost to make and so the cheaper we can sell them for!

if you don’t know yet, the calendar is a collaborative project between multiple phandom artists to replace the official dan and phil calendar seeing as they’re not doing one next year.
